; ============================================================================
; d3d12proxy.def
;
; Module definition file for the d3d12 proxy DLL.
; This explicitly exports the standard d3d12.dll entry points under their
; exact (case-sensitive) names, so the application sees the same export
; table it would expect from the real DLL.
;
; CRITICAL: ordinals must match the real d3d12.dll's, not just the names.
; Some callers (D3D12Core / redistributable bootstrapping code, some system
; DLLs) import d3d12.dll's exports BY ORDINAL rather than by name. If our
; proxy exports the same names but under different (linker-assigned)
; ordinals, that ordinal-based import resolution fails at load time with
; STATUS_ORDINAL_NOT_FOUND / ERROR_PROC_NOT_FOUND, even though the names
; themselves all resolve fine via GetProcAddress-by-name. This is exactly
; what happened here: x64dbg reported STATUS_ORDINAL_NOT_FOUND on our
; d3d12.dll for ordinals 101/102.
;
; Ordinals below match the standard 64-bit d3d12.dll layout (confirmed via
; dumpbin /exports on a real system d3d12.dll -- stable across the versions
; that expose these particular exports; GetBehaviorValue/SetAppCompatString
; Pointer/D3D12PIX*/D3D12DeviceRemovedExtendedData are intentionally NOT
; exported here since nothing in this proxy chain calls them by ordinal or
; by name, and D3D12On7 redistributables typically don't ship them anyway).
;
; The LIBRARY name below is purely informational for some linkers; the
; actual output file name is still chosen with the "-o" flag at link time
; (it should be "d3d12.dll" for deployment).
; ============================================================================

LIBRARY d3d12

EXPORTS
    D3D12CreateDevice                              @101
    D3D12GetDebugInterface                         @102
    D3D12CreateRootSignatureDeserializer           @107
    D3D12CreateVersionedRootSignatureDeserializer  @108
    D3D12SerializeRootSignature                    @115
    D3D12SerializeVersionedRootSignature            @116
    D3D12EnableExperimentalFeatures                @110
